        "body": "<p>This way you can use something and then add it to the layout of the screen you want it to appear.<\/p>\n<pre><code>class TestBannerView @JvmOverloads constructor(context: Context,\n                                                          attrs: AttributeSet? = null,\n                                                          defStyle: Int = 0,\n                                                          defStyleRes: Int = 0) : FrameLayout(context, attrs, defStyle, defStyleRes) {\ninit {\n    LayoutInflater.from(context).inflate(R.layout.test_banner_view, this, true)\n     }\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
